            <title>[FELIX-4167] DeploymentAdmin tries to start/stop fragment bundles</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-4167</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Deployment Admin currently tries to start all bundles in a deployment package, including fragment bundles. Although this fails, the installation of the deployment package still succeeds. Nevertheless, it is sloppy to do this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
